																	"handle": "hf23f888bgc586g4e38gb785gbfffd0a48c28",
																	"value": "You're mad. I'd try to get you help, but there's nowhere to take you, and no time to figure out what the fuck to do. I guess this is goodbye. Don't struggle - it'll only hurt more.",
